data.description: Situated in the charming Summerwood community, this home offers the convenience of new construction without the wait. Located in the desirable Grassfield district, this nearly new construction boasts 5 spacious bedrooms, including a large FROG that can double as a 6th bedroom or bonus room. With a bedroom on the first floor featuring a full bath and the remaining 4 on the second floor, the property offers ample space. The gourmet kitchen, breakfast nook, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large pantry all seamlessly flow into the great room. Outside, a pleasant deck and a spacious backyard that backs up to the woods provide a tranquil setting with no visible neighbors. Explore nearby trails and discover the array of additional amenities this property has to offer! Be sure and look into assumable loan at 4.25% with payment of $3585 with 80k down.
